Class SAMLJwtTokenHandler

  • public class SAMLJwtTokenHandler
extends cat.gencat.ctti.canigo.arch.security.rest.authentication.jwt.JwtTokenHandler
    Extends JwtTokenHandler and allows creation of JWT tokens which contain claims that come from a SAMLUser claims obtained when validating an SAML assertion.

    cscanigo
